{"tid":1404588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家幫下被拉嘅機師","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:48:28.000Z","uid":94033,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db37632d5f5371963b6e05f8fd777c2afd68b462","tid":1404588,"uid":94033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"國泰機師廖頌賢保釋候審後，好多藍屍去國泰同埋民航處投訴，唔俾廖先生繼續返工。而家國泰都好大壓力，請大家寫個電郵俾國泰 ir@cathaypacific.com 以及民航處熱線 enquiry@cad.gov.hk ，支持廖機師恢復工作。<br />\n<br />\n國泰另有呢位專責呢種case嘅高層：<br />\nPaul Loo<br />\npaul_loo@cathaypacific.com <br />\n<br />\n實體信可以奇到:<br />\nChief Customer and Commercial Officer <br />\n6th Floor Cathay Pacific City 8 Scenic Roar<br />\nHong Kong International Airport<br />\nLantau, Hong Kong <br />\n<br />\n範本:<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n有關國泰機師涉「暴動罪」事宜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人從新聞得悉  貴公司有一名機師涉及本港近日「反送中」的事宜，並被控暴動罪。本人明白  貴公司有既定程序處理職員的事宜，不過希望  貴公司處理時，可考慮其機師現階段並未定罪，仍是良好公民，不要因社會評論而胡亂對機師作出不必要 及不公平的制裁，以免影響  貴公司在港良心僱主的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空公司<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n        市民XXX啟<br />\n<br />\n二零一九年八月X日<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cdfa75f6e942e3e99dc879ef8a5b95fe316b72","tid":1404588,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343ee37cb254fe8ba0fde82927460ead3cfb0cc9","tid":1404588,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:46:20.000Z","msg":"推 send咗"},{"pid":"6717f15ab5e0d8d75a9e86503242ff374859d2fd","tid":1404588,"uid":269428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk